videos.description: Aliyah Boston does it on both ends during South Carolina's early 10-0 run vs. Duke.
videos.headline: Aliyah Boston drains the 3 and comes up with the block on the other end

videos.description: South Carolina's Brea Beal comes up with the Duke turnover and goes coast to coast for the layup.
videos.headline: Brea Beal takes it the length of the court to cap off 16-0 run

videos.description: Elizabeth Balogun scores for Duke after over eight minutes without a field goal.
videos.headline: Elizabeth Balogun finally ends the scoring drought for Duke

videos.description: Celeste Taylor splashes in the triple as Duke cuts into South Carolina's lead.
videos.headline: Celeste Taylor drains the 3-pointer to bring Duke within 10

videos.description: Duke pulls to within seven of South Carolina after Shayeann Day-Wilson's four-point play.
videos.headline: Shayeann Day-Wilson drains the stepback 3 plus the foul

videos.description: Aliyah Boston scores 19 points as South Carolina tops Duke at Cameron Indoor Stadium.
